      <title>中国制定金融风险“一省一策”方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/china-frames-one-province-one-policy-plan-for-financial-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份报告称，在官员承诺建立解决地方债务问题的机制大约一个月后，中国监管机构希望各省拿出自己的计划来应对金融风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/china-frames-one-province-one-policy-plan-for-financial-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 06:59:27 GMT</pubDate>
