      <title>恒大面临避免被香港法院清算的最后机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-02/evergrande-faces-final-chance-to-avoid-liquidation-by-hk-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[违约标志着中国房地产危机的关键时刻，两年后，这家全球负债最重的开发商可能正在走向另一个惨淡的里程碑：清算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-02/evergrande-faces-final-chance-to-avoid-liquidation-by-hk-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
